Package io.permazen.vaadin.app

Support for Permazen GUI applications based on Vaadin.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GUIConfig
    Configuration object for the Permazen GUI application.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractUI
    Support superclass for Vaadin UI implementations.
    GUIUIProvider
    UIProvider for this GUI.
    HorizontalLine
    Simple horizontal line.
    JObjectEditorWindow
    GUI window for editing a database object.
    Main
    GUI main entry point.
    MainPanel
    Main GUI panel containing the object chooser, object table, buttons, and expresssion text area.
    MainUI
    Main GUI UI component.
    ReferenceFieldField
    A Vaadin Field that edits a database object reference.
    SimpleFieldFieldBuilder
    Builds Fields for editing JSimpleField values.
